  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "BARISTA CUM SERVICE CREW",
  "description": "<h2> <strong>Barista cum Service Crew (Cafe)</strong></h2><p>We’re looking for a <strong>friendly and reliable Barista cum Service Crew</strong> to join our café team! No worries if you’re new — <strong>training will be provided</strong> 😊</p><h3><strong>What You’ll Do</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Prepare coffee and drinks (training provided)</p></li><li><p>Take customer orders and serve food & drinks</p></li><li><p>Greet customers and provide friendly service</p></li><li><p>Keep tables, counter, and café area clean</p></li><li><p>Help with simple food plating (cakes, light meals,Dessert)</p></li><li><p>Operate cashier / POS system</p></li><li><p>Support teammates during busy periods</p></li></ul><h3><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Positive attitude and friendly personality</p></li><li><p>Willing to learn and work as a team</p></li><li><p>Able to work in a fast-paced café environment</p></li><li><p>Basic communication skills</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Working Hours</strong></h3><p><ul><li>5 days work week (weekends & public holidays applies)</li><li>9 hours daily</li><li>Full-time / Part-time available</li></ul></p><h3><strong>Why Join Us</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Training provided (coffee & service)</p></li><li><p>Friendly and supportive team</p></li><li><p>Staff meals / staff drinks</p></li><li><p>Career growth opportunities<br /></p></li></ul><p>📍 <strong>Location:</strong>Punggol Coast mall<br /><br />📩 <strong>Apply via:</strong> whatsapp 90996648</p>",
